{"tid":1421314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦發言人：港人領憤怒孩子回家　向破壞分子怒吼","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:18:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":621,"uniUserReply":153,"replies":[{"pid":"8f74c1350ec2f7f1b87efc46e7c892a80fc56842","tid":1421314,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"港澳辦新聞發言人楊光表示，香港局勢發展至今天，市民最重要的任務是回復秩序，呼籲正義力量站出來，維護美好家園。<br />\n<br />\n他又要求市民，要像慈愛的媽媽一樣，把他們充滿莫名憤怒的孩子領回家，也要向阻止港鐵車門關上的破壞分子怒吼。楊光重申，不要低估守護香港的強大正義力量，也不要低估中央維護香港繁榮穩定的決心和力量。<br />\n<br />\n楊光出席國新辦舉行的媒體吹風會時表示，請香港市民要冷靜思考，如果亂局不可收拾，誰是最終受害者和受益，強調玩火者必自焚，該來的懲罰終將到來，支持香港特區政府、司法機構和警察，對所有參與暴力，一律追究法律責任，特別是幕後策劃組織和指揮者，亦請他們不會誤判形勢。"},{"pid":"42c0efe4f717659cfe2064ba3ee0d1b64f1f0f90","tid":1421314,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473040-20190806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473040-20190806.htm&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=11c7c341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473040-20190806.htm&h=33d8c1c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473040-20190806.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9e52024e0a0f72285d9872d5733e230acba8fcef","tid":1421314,"uid":35005,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"Zzz....."},{"pid":"12bada43d4a281c1afb2b226f129accf61760c17","tid":1421314,"uid":26385,"like":416,"dislike":0,"score":416,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"中國吆喝一聲 嚇得香港屁滾尿流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44470db29d5b2c001f2996e22c3c1828198f52c","tid":1421314,"uid":705,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"從來無低估，係出兵就快"},{"pid":"ad50a87e2c5ffc17b340