e":"2019-08-06T07:56:30.000Z","msg":"你d記者會唔該進化啦"},{"pid":"ec84d142df89c42e9e6f376c344270e93ea38d3b","tid":1421314,"uid":248402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a46598b8d90680443640c2a2a5b50831a1e61930","tid":1421314,"uid":113902,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"ad50a87e2c5ffc17b340a300a71a4d35497c3c20","tid":1421314,"uid":52271,"like":243,"dislike":0,"score":243,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:44:50.000Z","msg":"又慈母<br />\n咁鍾意做人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"乜有做仔既年齡大過老母既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"唔通係後母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399ff7e76f78fd8b7fbae3cb0b0cc39338da62ca","tid":1421314,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"即係大規模出老黑"},{"pid":"2a779d88c8a309b5e7ce1388c3e1bdff3228ec31","tid":1421314,"uid":199532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;如果亂局不可收拾，誰是最終受害者和受益&rdquo;<br />\n最大受傷者: 支那<br />\n最大受益者: 香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51f2cd299ab178dd248572372a86bd0983b4b25","tid":1421314,"uid":274278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"哇<br />\n一睇就知係送俾黑幫用既暗號黎啦<br />\n之後黑幫就攞正牌 只要大叫&quot;守護香港正義的力量&quot;就可以光天化日下打人了"},{"pid":"5f6d21ba3090e92a42adc1f8d976114c63b9aebc","tid":1421314,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"各位小心安全，佢講嘅正義力量，係指黑力量，肯定唔係唔同政見嘅善男信女<br />\n<br />\n如果真係咁多支持你嘅人士，點解咁耐以嚟都無幾多個自發性咁行出嚟？請得郁嘅唔係老就殘(腦殘)，仲要安排埋接送<br />\n<br />\n成日屈行出嚟嘅黃絲係收錢，人又多物資又多，仲有大量街坊隨時行落街聲援。咁到底張單係邊個勢力埋？每人每次收一千都無人埋得掂張單，仲吹水話幾千。只有一直被政府愚弄嘅大陸人同腦殘嘅人先會信"},{"pid":"3552fc568824f8a587696caf254238605aee30ef","tid":1421314,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike